parece en días o semanas","guid":"Iu4_qPOST1Kt6hQO30i7jg","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"• Vértigo constante por meses ≠ vestibular","guid":"Poc18amCOFouwCze4nvdvg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"• Desequilibrio constante → Sí puede ser vestibular","guid":"KnU2aht5CtcLj9YGOUYPCg","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"138","text":"Duración y frecuencia\\Nayudan a dx ","guid":"Gp_1hTboK-V_5_YDmZPgyw","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Episodios <1 min : VPPB","guid":"hUdf_VymJJodEfiSJDWHzw","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"• Único episodio de\\Nminutos-horas","guid":"jImeDHPIBlJJQ2Gg51zQTQ","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• Migraña vestibular","guid":"Eij__CbBaLcq9kxbwTnIng","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"• Isquemia transitoria (laberinto/tronco encefálico)","guid":"BcDRZVRpPt8CU9yMVAGFgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"• Episodios recurrentes\\Nde horas","guid":"HS-DHwRZFWrE1Zxzn_hfVA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Enfermedad de Ménière","guid":"HxwoL9zw8PvjT1EECn_B4g","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"• Migraña vestibular","guid":"xVnR43pUp4V0AwcHc2H0MQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"143","text":"• Episodios prolongados\\N(> días)","guid":"l8F_qpUdeoHvN_XAhR5iQg","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Neuronitis vestibular","guid":"WgazH5J5cc3b42SikJf7lg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"• Esclerosis múltiple","guid":"4IaUGUdOIiXqkjtwONOvDQ","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"• Infarto troncoencefálico/cerebeloso","guid":"FQ5fKrUAdQFIXMfkZJVt3Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"129","text":"3.1.2. Factores que\\NAgravan o Provocan","guid":"k9XhqRAt1p9Cs0H-NKbpnQ","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"• Todo vértigo empeora con movimientos cefálicos","guid":"PmbOYahKJkYTU_bBetXSkw","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"• Movimientos específicos pueden sugerir daño otolítico","guid":"uJp_fuNITLc7EG_VoE_uIw","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• Ej. Pararse en un barco, cambios de velocidad en ascensor","guid":"xot7PT1-tX5ET6nMWgPqPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"155","text":"• Movimientos que\\Nprovocan VPPB:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Girar en la cama","guid":"noLozvPbVO0NA7PDWakWHg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Extender el cuello","guid":"V9mRzc6N4pC7S-kr4jgbLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"155","text":"• Agravado por tos, estornudos,\\Nesfuerzo, ruidos fuertes ","guid":"ayJBChFAz8W-8CEcfJqzAw","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Fístula perilinfática","guid":"EaCoWBJGlJobWkWB3mUBQw","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"• Dehiscencia del canal semicircular superior","guid":"4o0yaNMNwYq2m1j954cXmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"155","text":"• Historia de trauma craneal","guid":"QIftAn3p_Zyky54a2PQn4w","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"• Causa de vértigo postraumático","guid":"OdK5fxLlcMFDxaqexDZ67w","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"155","text":"• Barotrauma, cirugía de oído medio, maniobras de Valsalva","guid":"D2lH9mG6-zLmHMqhEOronQ","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Posible fístula perilinfática","guid":"RRTHglXHh52OsL33PIDHnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"155","text":"• Mareo por estímulos visuales (alfombras\\Ncon patrones, pantallas grandes)","guid":"1v1ucE8YQvwiPD-tl1XI-g","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Mareo postural perceptual\\Npersistente (Vértigo visual)","guid":"CBSpYypQbsMQccuiTw3Y6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"155","text":"• Hiperextensión cervical reciente + dolor","guid":"YhsueBRQ8BncJJO_VBCeFA","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Disección de arteria vertebral → isquemia tronco/laberinto","guid":"EWiZ43_s3kcymFjLcpWWBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"155","text":"• Síntomas virales recientes:  Neuronitis vestibular","guid":"-DSmDxxROmme6NE2U_k8Tg","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"• ⚠️ No siempre presente (<50%)","guid":"qRsF6yBpggewJgqWGrh7Ww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"129","text":"3.1.3. Síntomas\\NAsociados","guid":"hsXZUt_3PD3tXvskHso0qA","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• Déficit neurológico focal :\\NAccidente cerebrovascular\\Nvertebrobasilar","guid":"R3FT7cfHcMgNM9-arfcRGQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"• Diplopía, disartria, disfagia, paresia, hipoestesia","guid":"O8fOq49xjupQ4zBv1LPGVg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"• Infarto cerebeloso → Puede presentarse solo con vértigo","guid":"K54qQV2KBLiKLjzuDr6m2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"• Esclerosis múltiple : Otros signos neurológicos previos/asociados","guid":"yg3uCRFS57FWamJODU6C5A","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"• Hipoacusia + acúfenos : Lesión periférica","guid":"AibNqCny30yfIOc4iabFzA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"175","text":"• Plenitud aural : Enfermedad de Ménière","guid":"WUR6q9alVMxW0DKq0azTiA","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"175","text":"• Cefalea + fotofobia + fonofobia : Migraña vestibular","guid":"8LIQeT0JgAMtQFSo2O5q9g","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"175","text":"• Disnea, palpitaciones, sudoración : Crisis de pánico","guid":"LJ6nHr0ptpwl62uGtLn9mg","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"• ⚠️ Vértigo vestibular severo también puede desencadenarlos","guid":"Yv7dvaO7F8kL-JMrWWrKhw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"129","text":"3.1.4.\\NAntecedentes\\NMédicos","guid":"quCx2fAxJgTQviN30F5oDQ","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• Migraña previa : Posible vértigo migrañoso","guid":"KegWX0NQcZukn5mBAijfEQ","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"• Factores de riesgo cardiovascular (HTA, DM,\\Ntabaquismo, enfermedad vascular previa)","guid":"n-68Q1cXabwwrr3XFgwTdQ","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Alto riesgo de AIT/isquemia vertebrobasilar","guid":"yUubhQS_nBgvBkZVpeAOIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"• Trauma craneal previo","guid":"94EdlKbnzhmrba2qyHrblQ","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Asociado a VPPB y mareo postural perceptual persistente","guid":"xwNjmAmZD2ahtdVX7ZjV6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"185","text":"• Fármacos\\Nototóxicos","guid":"4mKMF86PckI_IMnxPSTo9A","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Vestibulotoxicidad : Aminoglucósidos, cisplatino","guid":"ncfrkEGT4rbbI9wuxpnSHQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"• Toxicidad cerebelosa : Fenitoína","guid":"P0dDuHIX2JUVnL-2wMxrKA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"128","text":"3.2. EXAMEN\\NFÍSICO","guid":"UFWKQPP-sc9z1TlqQ7nE4A","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"• Confirmar\\Ndisfunción\\Nvestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"• Diferenciar etiología central\\Nvs periférica (Tabla 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"194","text":"3.2.1. Nistagmo","guid":"1GJgWRhVdDgwzXhMb9yvMQ","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"• Oscilación\\Nrítmica ocular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"• Reflejo vestíbulo-ocular (VOR)\\Nafectado en lesiones agudas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"• Nistagmo espontáneo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"197","text":"• Lesión periférica 🡺 Fase rápida\\Nalejada del lado afectado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"197","text":"• Obedece la Ley de Alexander\\N(aumenta con mirada en\\Ndirección de la fase rápida)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"197","text":"• Diferencias\\Ncentrales vs\\Nperiféricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"197","text":"• Periférico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"197","text":"• Horizonte-torsional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"197","text":"• Se suprime con\\Nfijación visual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"197","text":"• NO es vertical puro","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"197","text":"• Central:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"197","text":"• Puede ser\\Nvertical/torsional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"197","text":"• NO se suprime\\Ncon fijación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"197","text":"• Cambia de\\Ndirección con la\\Nmirada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"194","text":"3.2.2.\\NEquilibrio y\\NMarcha","guid":"lcaFY3g0f1I0OmjHf75sAQ","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Trastornos periféricos 🡺\\Ninclinación hacia lado afectado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"• Prueba de Romberg 🡺 caída\\Nhacia el lado afectado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"• Lesión cerebelosa 🡺\\Nimposibilidad de caminar sin caer","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"194","text":"3.2.3. Signos\\NNeurológicos","guid":"WDozHo2yy1oopF7Y-798_g","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Déficit de pares craneales,\\Nataxia, reflejos anormales 🡺","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"• Sospecha de\\Netiología central","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"216","text":"• Síndrome de Wallenberg\\N(infarto bulbar lateral) 🡺","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"216","text":"• Hipoestesia facial, ptosis,\\Nanisocoria, diplopía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"216","text":"• Infarto cerebeloso\\Nmedial/inferior 🡺","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"216","text":"• Puede no tener signos\\Nneurológicos adicionales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"194","text":"3.2.4. Examen Auditivo","guid":"OGMO_X-ogCEFi5lZjQAz7w","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"• Pruebas de\\NWeber y Rinne","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":"• Pérdida auditiva neurosensorial\\Nunilateral 🡺 Lesión periférica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"223","text":"• Dx diferencial con audiometría +\\NRM/TC si no hay causa obvia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"194","text":"3.2.5. Maniobras\\NDiagnósticas","guid":"LYrAru2qvbBYo32t6I6QiA","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"• Dix-Hallpike (VPPB,\\Ncanal posterior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"• Latencia + fatiga + reversión\\Nal sentarse → VPPB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"• Head Impulse Test (VOR,\\Nlesión vestibular periférica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"227","text":"• Mov. sacádico correctivo\\N→ Lesión periférica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"227","text":"• Normal → Sospecha\\Nde causa central","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"227","text":"• HINTS (Head Impulse,\\NNistagmo, Test de Skew)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"227","text":"• Normal en impulso cefálico +\\Nnistagmo cambiante + skew\\Ndeviation → Central","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"235","parent":"194","text":"3.2.6. Pruebas\\NVestibulares\\NAdicionales","guid":"mH3ZraZEuQDtdf_epEMUkQ","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Prueba del balde (visual\\Nvertical subjetiva)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"• Desviación ipsilateral → Lesión\\Nvestibular periférica o bulbar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"235","text":"• Desviación contralateral → Lesión\\Nmesencefálica/cerebelosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"235","text":"• Nistagmo post-shaking\\N(asimetría vestibular)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"235","text":"• Pruebas calóricas\\N(raramente en consulta)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"235","text":"• Ausencia de respuesta en un lado →\\NLesión vestibular periférica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"0","text":"4. PRUEBAS\\NDIAGNÓSTICAS","guid":"fJJucF11lVX-oZE_brTXyw","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"4.1. IMÁGENES\\NCEREBRALES","guid":"k_fzkUFs3yJlMo--R0UU6w","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Indicadas si:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"• Sospecha de causa central","guid":"vMLBJjNmK7usJpqDaPXTsg","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"• Sospecha de schwannoma vestibular","guid":"nTJOWTJCRU6neNU_r8sW-w","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"244","text":"• Examen físico inconsistente con lesión periférica","guid":"NTLoealHFh89ts-EeU0G9Q","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"244","text":"• Factores de riesgo vascular prominentes","guid":"1N5oIZ97n1eZwwyzmWwfBg","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"244","text":"• Síntomas neurológicos asociados","guid":"w6kZuxT-xAGVROolhUUbww","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"244","text":"• Paciente no puede caminar","guid":"gqWgiCR4fC4QJxVHzJoaVQ","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"244","text":"• Nueva cefalea junto con vértigo","guid":"SOUZ962UDRjmstO30MHhww","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"243","text":"4.1.1. Elección\\Nde imagen","guid":"ggJ-HfJQ5wQ_6Kvxv1Vcag","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"• RM + MRA\\N(1° opción)","guid":"tNcJ7XtE8o4ph7VMBwMNpQ","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"• Detecta infartos de fosa posterior desde el día 1","guid":"NoghiYVNOOX8lb3PPrlfuQ","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"• MRA: Sensibilidad/especificidad > 95% para estenosis/oclusión circulación posterior","guid":"IIPi0ljmnlergXul10Mwog","children":[]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"252","text":"• TAC (cortes finos cerebelo)\\N→ Alternativa si:","guid":"759-_s91j0dxnGfsTS4WUg","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"• RM no disponible","guid":"hyDXQpiYvBQfbyOIVRoDsA","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"256","text":"• Px con implantes metálicos","guid":"w2xYpMdfZgH78puM2YDSog","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"256","text":"• Limitaciones\\Ndel TAC:","guid":"lQ6EzYSREmkHs43o90gsBg","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"• Menos sensible para infarto temprano/masas pequeñas","guid":"3LuEhOmBAwDfbUIqeO6-vQ","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"• Detecta hemorragia inmediatamente","guid":"F846GQ13edWbDEM0R0iVrA","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"242","text":"4.2. ELECTRONISTAGMOGRAFÍA (ENG)\\NY VIDEO-NISTAGMOGRAFÍA (VNG)","guid":"Z6ZTZVWbvFZkILJBBbGEkg","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• Registra y cuantifica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"• Nistagmo espontáneo","guid":"Te3I3zhU-vHRT_dTtRLLRg","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"• Nistagmo inducido","guid":"R5uOKrsd45S1lJX2fjKw6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"262","text":"• Utilidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Diferenciar causas centrales vs periféricas","guid":"IWIpDsZvMAOxyOwbn-5JfA","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"262","text":"• Pruebas\\Nincluidas:","guid":"QIgocsr9XHzgI0bGzc0JmA","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Screening motor ocular","guid":"_5JwFhdjEA4OwKb58O3dXw","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"• Pruebas posicionales","guid":"l4CwPB9GU1Y3AfiH3f4UZA","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"268","text":"• Prueba de impulso cefálico","guid":"fj_nft4eH7_N08MzM40NAA","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"268","text":"• Pruebas calóricas","guid":"0X47DKbF8zbr3wl0Z2HSfw","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"268","text":"• Prueba rotacional","guid":"7lZ2yvCiuHkubRtq6eICOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"262","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• Síntomas persistentes >1-2 semanas","guid":"VUDNjkmLLw9ZPS0Aw-t6ww","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"• No responde a tratamiento inicial (meclizina, betahistina)","guid":"ahb-bm9KjDwzQ8tga3FIMQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"274","text":"• Síntomas incapacitantes","guid":"6kAPMgQgCfNaHMDtx4eJ9g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"242","text":"4.3. POTENCIALES MIOGÉNICOS\\NVESTIBULARES (VEMPs)","guid":"tIpR9sEZh7tAbGfjXJ2Xeg","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"• Evalúan función otolítica","guid":"mitqk7XkDW_rrLpKxmtEvA","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"278","text":"• Tipos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"• cVEMPs (potenciales cervicales) : Evalúan sáculo","guid":"1FrPoODFfnfM9pItPj6iJQ","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"• Estimulación sonora → Registro en ECM ipsilateral","guid":"X1vO7Mc7KxsS4C1XcblQlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"280","text":"• oVEMPs (potenciales oculares) : Evalúan utrículo","guid":"1A2xNBYFo6kTjaEUmyBUlQ","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"• Registro en músculos extraoculares durante vibración cefálica","guid":"xYEtWvPllb3cBdydlVNaIQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"285","parent":"278","text":"• Usos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"• cVEMP con umbral reducido : Dehiscencia del canal semicircular superior","guid":"EHQNwHDPA0mwDzpy8Yz6UQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"242","text":"4.4. AUDIOMETRÍA","guid":"EIQ6ixWoklr6xXJTneINGQ","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"• + sensible que pruebas de cabecera para hipoacusia","guid":"GnvFUkcju93o91637_33Gw","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"• Evalúa:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"290","parent":"289","text":"• Grado de pérdida auditiva","guid":"wJyaOSomtWnjnKzIeY_B5g","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"289","text":"• Frecuencias altas y bajas","guid":"f7np6zVrD5Do9dz6aaC4tg","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"289","text":"• Presencia de reclutamiento","guid":"itDQo2uebVKKqcgocTJVNw","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"289","text":"• Reconocimiento de palabras","guid":"NLcLpd34ymsaGY5-O5eYFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"287","text":"• Utilidad en vértigo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"• Dx diferencial","guid":"IbUhv0QIq1916B_NGQCaTQ","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"• Sospecha de schwannoma vestibular → Detecta hipoacusia unilateral","guid":"6JNCV_59tSkHkz0KCeGBFQ","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"• Hipoacusia neurosensorial de baja frecuencia → Sugiere enfermedad de Ménière","guid":"HuoNZrofCQkYxqP6hsscLg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"242","text":"4.5. POTENCIALES EVOCADOS AUDITIVOS\\NDEL TRONCO CEREBRAL (BAEPs)","guid":"BRouYiXKEUr2NCkrZWd59Q","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"• Sensibilidad 90-95% para\\Nschwannomas vestibulares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"298","text":"• Detecta alteraciones en la\\Ntransmisión auditiva troncoencefálica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"298","text":"• ⚠️ Uso limitado 🡺 No\\Nespecífico para dx vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"298","text":"• No se usa de rutina en\\Nevaluación de vértigo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"303","parent":"0","text":"5. ENFOQUE\\NDIAGNÓSTICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"304","parent":"303","text":"5.1. PASO 1: CONFIRMACIÓN\\NDE VÉRTIGO","guid":"7vHo_ss9GCLCVh2uAlSM2Q","children":[{"id":"305","parent":"304","text":"• Diferenciar vértigo de otros tipos de mareo","guid":"7WvnKJvA4tHAT_3Qu67h3Q","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"304","text":"• Características distintivas","guid":"Ndj3NQdKZTROT6zCbxgaHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"307","parent":"303","text":"5.2. PASO 2: CLASIFICACIÓN\\NCENTRAL VS PERIFÉRICO","guid":"rkfWe5edGnz4lGZ7074Guw","children":[{"id":"308","parent":"307","text":"• Basado en:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"• Características del nistagmo","guid":"9mQt_kRP6nO2vjTZcVLx5A","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"308","text":"• Inestabilidad postural","guid":"6CkxRdTl-6F_xwrE2lW0lA","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"308","text":"• Hipoacusia o acúfenos","guid":"5xUmFhzNsCkkMG6RlYijCA","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"308","text":"• Déficit neurológico","guid":"TM7FDjrTnhvnrQm0GmdC8A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"313","parent":"303","text":"5.3. PASO 3: ANÁLISIS DEL\\NCURSO TEMPORAL","guid":"OeZwmeM9lP4tOSrWVsmJgQ","children":[{"id":"314","parent":"313","text":"• Los px describen mejor la duración que la calidad del síntoma","guid":"Y1cswyQhxrXpy1HgrOFB3A","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"313","text":"5.3.1. Vértigo\\Nagudo sostenido","guid":"DPjluriPA-rLCq7peNgcdQ","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"• Dx más comunes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"317","parent":"316","text":"• Neuronitis vestibular","guid":"yqvU_SBKjuZXCNuJpROrHQ","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"316","text":"• Esclerosis múltiple","guid":"r-d80XYihKM3M2DEiI17sg","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"316","text":"• Accidente cerebrovascular (tronco/cerebelo)","guid":"mmbTJAQWXcPaYbpNFV9DXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"315","text":"• Evaluación adicional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"• FR cardiovascular + déficits neurológicos → Sospecha vascular","guid":"CtfFLu6nNUS-EF5tTajkNA","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"320","text":"• Test\\NHINTS","guid":"1RVFvbLi3iegcuOyQ-9uJw","children":[{"id":"323","parent":"322","text":"• Impulso cefálico anormal : Periférico (Neuronitis vestibular)","guid":"P-na-I_X-0kzX6TjPCDnJg","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"322","text":"• Impulso cefálico normal : Central (ACV, desmielinización)","guid":"0FTPdvSF7OsdqJBmR70keA","children":[]}]},{"id":"325","parent":"320","text":"• RM focalizada en tronco encefálico si sospecha de causa central","guid":"N_5Kp4agLsi0FNmVoPoYnA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"326","parent":"313","text":"5.3.2. Vértigo episódico","guid":"pjFJP7R1jGDT0RTv97JZKA","children":[{"id":"327","parent":"326","text":"• Clasificación por duración + síntomas asociados","guid":"BwzsQS8CeDvOa4vreKyG6w","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"326","text":"📌 Vértigo muy breve (<1 min) +\\NMovimientos predecibles : VPPB","guid":"_rm3jI6d2qzhr2fJvVr5rw","children":[{"id":"329","parent":"328","text":"• Confirmación: Maniobra de Dix-Hallpike","guid":"4c3_SOblbS4lCkGNqhCukQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"330","parent":"326","text":"📌 Episodios más largos (min-horas)\\N→ Diferenciar por síntomas","guid":"P9MMZ13Lnt3ptGhc7HcDLQ","children":[{"id":"331","parent":"330","text":"• Cefalea : Migraña vestibular","guid":"svLPVxKRh6PpWIvEBTKW5w","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"330","text":"• Hipoacusia unilateral + acúfenos + plenitud aural : Enfermedad de Ménière","guid":"0j5zzJQQksbeCwBehDZ1_Q","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"330","text":"• Déficit neurológico troncoencefálico : Isquemia vertebrobasilar (AIT)","guid":"BKACCt8z30xBg6Rcu3nuag","children":[]}]},{"id":"334","parent":"326","text":"📌 Vértigo postraumático : Ver evaluación separada","guid":"9l9-yn3iHekj1TiZBvNJIg","children":[]},{"id":"335","parent":"326","text":"📌 Lista más amplia de causas en revisión separada","guid":"ZjUdpnqUUKEr1B3roYSzAw","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":335,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neurología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"UTD. Vertigo-2025","id":"map_1463","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"UTD. Vertigo-2025"}